Files derived from and modified relative to upstream AniSOAP:

- anisoap/representations/radial_basis.py
  Added PyTorch linear algebra, batched Gaussian-parameter evaluation, and
  device propagation.

- anisoap/representations/ellipsoidal_density_projection.py
  Added batched pair extraction, batched Rust moment evaluation, PyTorch tensor
  contractions, and scatter-based feature aggregation.

- rust/ellip_expansion/compute_moments.rs
  Added batched moment evaluation across neighbor pairs.

- rust/lib.rs
  Added the PyO3 batch binding and GIL release around batched Rust work.

- Cargo.toml
  Added Rayon and repository-specific package metadata.

